==English==

===Etymology===
Irregular past participle of [[smite]]

Old English verb [[smittian]] - to pollute

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪtən|-ɪtən]]

===Adjective===
# Made irrationally enthusiastic
#: ''I was really smitten by the color combination, and soon repainted the entire house.''
# [[in love|In love]]
#: ''He was totally smitten by the librarian.''

